g src=\"https://na.cx/i/JZ4QfQ5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJZ4QfQ5.jpg&h=2f07bb61&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c5effe8d6f1fabcb8e12bec7daeb64e1689f1a0","tid":990832,"uid":36585,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:12:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.1823.gov.hk/big5/FAQ/018038/index.shtm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.1823.gov.hk%2Fbig5%2FFAQ%2F018038%2Findex.shtm&d=SEj7soRn3n8iCTLNY85HXjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=c28ac34c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.1823.gov.hk/big5/FAQ/018038/index.shtm</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19971ce61280c3921520a91950f78611be157d5d","tid":990832,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c5effe8d6f1fabcb8e12bec7daeb64e1689f1a0","tid":990832,"uid":36585,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:12:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.1823.gov.hk/big5/FAQ/018038/index.shtm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.1823.gov.hk%2Fbig5%2FFAQ%2F018038%2Findex.shtm&d=SEj7soRn3n8iCTLNY85HXjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=c28ac34c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.1823.gov.hk/big5/FAQ/018038/index.shtm</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:15:20.000Z","msg":"如遺失稅單<br />\n<br />\n市民可於辦公時間致電187 8022聯絡稅務局要求補發 (選擇語言 &gt; 按9字聯絡詢問處職員)(辦公時間: 星期一至五08:15-12:30及13:30-17:30(公眾假期除外)。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc1d283cec97e8a625b61f8d5f73e38cb08642a5","tid":990832,"uid":36585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f07b1dd822a3766531f30de50cd0ffef4a810d72","tid":990832,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:47:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f2R7hYF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff2R7hYF.png&h=193bc2f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴打，我轉左做合併報稅，咁樣情況係咪者係唔交稅有得申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:16:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.wfsfaa.gov.hk/careandshare/tc/faq.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wfsfaa.gov.hk%2Fcareandshare%2Ftc%2Ffaq.htm&d=SEj7soRn3n8iCTLNY85HXjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=88f4fe26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wfsfaa.gov.hk/careandshare/tc/faq.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n當夫婦的收入以合併評稅方式計算薪俸稅時，如何計算在本計劃下薪俸稅稅款寬減額的差額？<br />\n<br />\n本計劃以個人名義申請，因此夫婦必須分別提出申請。如夫婦的收入以合併評稅方式計算薪俸稅，而只有其中一方須繳交薪俸稅，並享有薪俸稅稅款寬減額。在這情況下，無須繳交薪俸稅的一方若符合計劃的其他資格（見答1），可提出申請。另一方的稅款寬減額如少於4,000元，並符合計劃的其他資格，亦可提出申請，獲發放的最高款額為4,000元扣除稅款寬減額後的餘額。實際獲發放款額則視乎每個個案是否須要再扣除差餉寬減額。<br />\n<br />\n個答案找死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0319d4d522f0d89d337074d850605a78114012a5","tid":990832,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c9b513432c0efb3bdb814bd3bd452710ad1be71","tid":990832,"uid":229677,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:41:08.000Z","msg":"上年收過退稅票小過4千就入得表<br />\n<br />\n利申稅就有份交，派錢就冇份<br />\n<br />\n契弟波正撚樣！屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:21:27.000Z","msg":"錯<br />\n係 tax computation 上面個稅務寬減少過4千先有"},{"pid":"fc3eed419f1f697130bfc0652593db46faf73634","tid":990832,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f07b1dd822a3766531f30de50cd0ffef4a810d72","tid":990832,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:47:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f2R7hYF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff2R7hYF.png&